        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p>
                <sic>
                    <addressee>Revd. Isaac Lesser</addressee>
                </sic>
                <placeName>Phil.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
                <date>Sept 8/620</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <add>בנחי זה רבה</add>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Baltimore</placeName>
                <date>Sept. 8, 1860</date>.</p>
            <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>, <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>,</p>
            <p>Dearest friend:</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Send the “Occident” from now on to <persName>Mr. Feist<lb/>
                    Herzberg</persName>, <placeName>Fayette Street, between Exeter and
                    High</placeName>. And send<lb/> to him each week regularly. Probably during the
                course of 7<lb/> week, I shall send you other subscribers. They are as good<lb/> as
                gold.</p>
            <p rend="indent(7)">With best wishes,</p>
            <p rend="indent(9)">Your friend,</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <persName role="author">Issacher Dr. Illoway</persName>
                <add>?</add>
            </p>
            <p>Very pressing</p>
        </body>
